title: For Sale:  Bushmaster ACR Enhanced
postcontent:
I'm selling my Bushmaster ACR enhanced model. The enhanced model comes with a folding stock, railed handguard, and AAC Blackout flash hider. Also included with this sale is the basic polymer handguard with small magpul rail segment attached, magpul MBUS flip up iron sights, and a magpul pmag 30 round magazine.

The ACR is operates with a piston system that is much cleaner and more reliable than a normal AR-15, and also allows for a folding stock.  The rifle also has a quick detach barrel system that allows the user to change calibers between .223, 300 blk, 6.8mm and 7.62x39 with the appropriate barrel assemblies without the need for any tools.

The rifle has around 2k rounds through it but is still in very good condition with only very small dings and scratches from use. There is wear on the moving parts such as the upper where the handguards slide on. The shell deflector also has a fair amount of wear as seen in the pics, but that is its purpose and can be replaced easily.

This rifle has been back to BM for the recall and has the titanium firing pin.

The rifle comes with everything shown in the pics, as well as the user manual. 

Only trade I would consider would be for a Sig 716 patrol newer model in black or a 16" barrel POF P308 in either black or NP3 (16" barrel, not the 14.5" with pinned break)
